---
title: Quick Vietnamese-Style Pork & Pear Tacos with Garlic Aioli
description: Sweet and savoury pork is the star of this crowd-pleasing meal. Easy and satisfying, the tacos come together in a snap, with lots
of veggies for everyone to build their own and join in the fun!
